The paper deals with image categorization, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves a combination of feature extraction, coding, and pooling, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the theoretical relationship between coding and pooling, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
